---
title: Stage Clock
---

The stage clock assigns additional `clock`
functionality to the Stage, such as an `fps()` method:

    stage = new Stage
    stage.clock.fps() // 59

The default delta is _one frame_ at 60fps.
    This is later updated - but is required early for mounted _fps_ tests.
